item.title: Ep 120: The Path to Finding True Love with Ben Nemtin & Vanessa Fitzgerald (PART 1)
item.description: In this special episode - recorded during their final trip before becoming parents - Ben and Vanessa join Melissa for a heartfelt conversation about their unforgettable time together at Intelligent Change in Ibiza. Ben and Vanessa open up about their path from a Hinge match to true love. Vanessa shares how shifting her mindset and letting go of ego and expectations, allowed her to approach dating with more openness and curiosity...
